org.obrel.space

Class RelationSpace<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.obrel.core.RelatedObject
      • org.obrel.space.RelationSpace<T>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Relatable, ObjectSpace<T>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    FileSystemSpace, HtmlSpace

    public class RelationSpace<T>
extends RelatedObject
implements ObjectSpace<T>
    An ObjectSpace implementation that is based on RelatedObject. It maps access URLs to the hierarchy of it's relations.
